{"tid":1256476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔眾籌全球登報反送中  一個上晝集資300萬","createTime":"2019-06-25T04:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T06:39:46.000Z","uid":622,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81032e449ba6b05cb418e04570bb290aac346a37","tid":1256476,"uid":622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190625&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59754467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190625%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59754467&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443v%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=658c94b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190625%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59754467&h=ee67c1f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190625&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59754467</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中浪潮持續，喺多次行動居功不少嘅連登仔又有新搞作。有網民發起眾籌300萬港幣，打算喺星期四G20峰會舉行當日，喺各國主要媒體登頭版廣告，呼籲國際社會關注《逃犯條例》修訂爭議同警暴問題。眾籌推出短短一個上晝，錄得超過1萬人捐款，籌款數字已經光速達標﹗<br />\n<br />\n發起眾籌嘅網民話，早前已經同美國《金融時報》（Financial Times）確認，對方會預留星期四（27號）美國版、亞洲版各1個版位，畀香港市民登反送中廣告，所須費用大概要港幣13萬幾。佢哋仲想喺美國、英國、日本、法國嘅主流報章登廣告，例如《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》等等，希望帶嚟更大影響力。<br />\n<br />\n發起登報嘅網民喺眾籌平台透露，香港捐款實在太踴躍，搞到付款平台Paypal以為有人洗黑錢，令捐款者一度只可以用信用咭、銀行咭科水。佢哋又話，會按最終籌集到嘅資金數目，決定向幾多國際傳媒登廣告，如果最終有餘款，籌得款項將會捐畀「反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金」。"},{"pid":"faca6b717c895c7249573efb3fe4f4c0c2c25847","tid":1256476,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dd1f9afc065038eea7c39c1c8c4a17df871ccc","tid":1256476,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"又宣傳連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19485e8e3fcee267cbcab5ddd0022722bf5afdb","tid":1256476,"uid":622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"香港電台 facebook 都有報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wb4VXe5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwb4VXe5.png&h=3f108f04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1bb4fe0c293ff0a1c35b8f05d42d0f53c290d3b","tid":1256476,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"高登同BB kingdom 㗎"}]}